\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

You will get much more maize if you use hybrid seed instead of recycled
 seed.
 Call the maize hot-line on 0200522420 free for more advice!
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

.
 About one month into the growing season, the following message was sent:
 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

When your maize is knee high, apply 1 water bottle cap of urea around each
 plant.
 Call the maize hot-line on 0200522420 free for more advice!
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

